    <item>
      <title>据称日本将考虑发行期限较短的债券</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/japan-is-said-to-consider-issuing-bonds-with-shorter-maturities</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博社看到的一份提案草案显示，日本财务省正在考虑将更多债券发行转向期限较短的债券，这是日本央行削减政府债券购买规模的重大变化。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/japan-is-said-to-consider-issuing-bonds-with-shorter-maturities</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 04:32:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国央行再次提出限制 140 亿美元刺激计划的提案</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/thai-central-bank-renews-case-to-limit-14-billion-cash-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国央行仍然坚决反对政府向几乎所有成年公民发放近 140 亿美元现金以重振消费活动的计划，称谨慎的做法是把重点放在有需要的人身上。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/thai-central-bank-renews-case-to-limit-14-billion-cash-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 03:37:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
